{"tid":2014462,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民建聯調查指七成受訪者認為假訊息激發年輕人犯法","createTime":"2020-05-13T04:58:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T12:36:22.000Z","uid":152476,"like":5,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"eee919a23ed72224f91c20a2844ca4bb5bff00a8","tid":2014462,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T04:58:28.000Z","msg":"一項調查發現，約7成的受訪者認為假訊息的傳播激發年輕人做出破壞社會秩序和犯法的行為，約6成受訪者認為一些社會領袖或政治人物鼓吹犯法的言論鼓動年輕人犯法。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯於5月初進行問卷調查，成功訪問了1385位12歲或以上的香港居民對香港「犯罪年輕化」的看法，結果又發現約65%受訪者認為，學校及教師向學生灌輸守法觀念的工作做得不足。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員周浩鼎認為，過去超過大半年內假消息多不勝數，網絡世界令假消息廣泛流傳，並鼓動市民參與違法行動，批評反對派政治領袖需為美化和合理化暴力行為負上責任。<br />\n<br />\n他建議，政府應制訂《防止網絡虛假資訊法例》打擊假新聞，在大、中、小學全面推行「守法教育」，向學生灌輸守法觀念，設立教材資料庫，要求學校及教師將教材上傳並公開讓公眾查閱，以及制訂失德及違法教師名冊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1525872-20200513.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1525872-20200513.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=RJ6DAKdT%2BAkj0rfdhPz9NRSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=e69fb24b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1525872-20200513.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=2da74d5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1525872-20200513.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec17c029e516d5979e0da5f337bde0e00aa634fe","tid":2014462,"uid":335303,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T05:00:09.000Z","msg":"約7成的<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撐警冇腦藍絲</span></span></strong>受訪者"},{"pid":"5563b93e8df3b89ba9c7d85431a979c2ac484a8e","tid":2014462,"uid":12628,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T05:02:25.000Z","msg":"一